### ========================================
### VALIDATION / ERROR CASES - Policy
### ========================================

### Policy for a non-existent partner - expected 400, "Partner with Id '999' does not exist."
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL0009999",
  "amount": 1000,
  "partnerId": 999
}

### PolicyNumber too short (fewer than 10 chars) - expected 400 (ModelState)
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "SHORT",
  "amount": 1000,
  "partnerId": 1
}

### PolicyNumber too long (more than 15 chars) - expected 400 (ModelState)
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL00000000000000000",
  "amount": 1000,
  "partnerId": 1
}

### Amount is zero - expected 400, "Amount must be greater than 0."
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL0000007",
  "amount": 0,
  "partnerId": 1
}

### Amount is negative - expected 400 (ModelState range check)
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL0000008",
  "amount": -50,
  "partnerId": 1
}

### Missing required field (policyNumber) - expected 400 (ModelState)
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500,
  "partnerId": 1
}

### Missing required field (amount) - expected 400, "Amount is required."
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL0000009",
  "partnerId": 1
}

### Missing required field (partnerId) - expected 400, "PartnerId is required."
POST {{Partners.Api_HostAddress}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "policyNumber": "POL0000010",
  "amount": 500
}

###